name: How are you my dear friend?
description:
Tanya Akhmetgalieva.
How are you my dear friend?
2022,
MP4, 1080 x 1920
20"

Tanya Akhmetgalieva (b. 1983, Kemerovo, Russia) multidisciplinary artist, works in painting, graphic arts, video, installation and digital art. Lives and works in St Petersburg and Moscow. Her works are presented in collections of such museums as The Moscow Museum of Modern Art (Moscow, Russia), The Russian Museum (St.Petersburg, Russia), The Tretyakov Gallery (Moscow, Russia), Kiasma (Helsinki, Finland), EMMA (Espoo, Finland), Turku Art Museum (Turku, Finland), as well as in private collections in Russia and Europe.
